üí° Lessons Learned
Always ensure that your Ethernet connection is functional and properly configured before assigning static IPs.
Verify that necessary services (pveproxy) are running and listening on the correct port.
Using a USB-C dock for Ethernet connection can work, but it may require additional troubleshooting.
üìú Conclusion
This guide summarizes how I configured and troubleshooted my Proxmox setup, overcoming networking issues and successfully accessing the web interface.
